title: Winners and Losers of Training Camp
itunes:title: Winners and Losers of Training Camp
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, & Gregg Rosenthal – recap all the latest news from around the NFL including the Dolphins picking up Jay Cutler and Anquan Boldin singing with the Bills. The heroes debate who has won and lost training camp thus far this season including Tom Savage, Colin Kaepernick and Cam Newton.
